data.description: Enjoy living that lake life with this 3 bedroom 2 bath mobile home.  Owners have taken excellent care of this home!  Newer laminate floors (2021) and roof (2020) PLUS new HVAC (2022) help keep you worry free and give you more time to enjoy Lake Marion!  No pesky mosquitoes here!  Watch your loved ones enjoy that oversized backyard from the comfort of your screened-in back porch complete with ceiling fans!  Storage won't be an issue for you!  There is an extra storage building or workshop - your choice!  You can also store your car PLUS your boat under the oversized carport.  Spring and Summer are coming!  Make sure you have your lake home ready to go before it's too late!
